    {
      "id": "candidate-node-sets-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Candidate Node Sets",
      "position": {
        "x": -1080,
        "y": 40
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "#1976d2",
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Candidate Node Sets\n\nThese are suggestions, not commitments.\n\nThe idea is to name promising **families of nodes** Twilite could grow into, instead of only arguing one node type at a time.\n\nStrong near-term candidates:\n- planning\n- knowledge / research\n- agent / prompting\n\nOthers may become important as the product surface expands.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
